            . I am a servant to Mr. Wright, who is an <rs id="t18150913-80-viclabel452" type="occupation">upholsterer</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18150913-80-victim721 t18150913-80-viclabel452"></join>. The prisoner came into the shop on the 7th of September, and asked my mistress for work; she told him, she had none for him; and just as she turned her back, he snatched up the oil-cloth, and ran off; he had got about two doors, when I stopped him, and brought him back.</p>
